    com.google.mu.util.Substring.Pattern.after​(Substring.Pattern)
    Replace foo.after(delim).from(input) with after(delim).from(input).map(foo::from).
    com.google.mu.util.Substring.Pattern.before​(Substring.Pattern)
    Replace foo.before(delim).from(input) with before(delim).from(input).map(foo::from).
    com.google.mu.util.Substring.Pattern.between​(Substring.Pattern, Substring.Pattern)
    Replace foo.between(x, y).from(input) with between(x, y).from(input).map(foo::from).
    com.google.mu.util.Substring.Pattern.replaceFrom​(String, char)
    Use Substring.Pattern.replaceFrom(String, CharSequence) instead.
    com.google.mu.util.Substring.Pattern.within​(Substring.Pattern)
    Replace foo.within(scope).from(input) with scope.from(input).map(foo::from).
    com.google.mu.util.Substring.regex​(Pattern)
    Use Substring.first(java.util.regex.Pattern) instead.
